From: Jon Medhurst <tixy@linaro.org>
Date: Tue, 17 Jul 2012 09:55:14 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 21/28] ARM: vexpress: Update TC2 memory to 2GB

Commit 6e21ce78667d9450787e3a4401d9d5c5fa9af748 from
git://git.linaro.org/kernel/linux-linaro-tracking.git

All TC2 boards 'in the wild' will have 2GB of memory, so lets make it
all available.

Signed-off-by: Jon Medhurst <tixy@linaro.org>
Signed-off-by: Guoqing Jiang <Guoqing.Jiang@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/vexpress-v2p-ca15-tc2.dts |    2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/vexpress-v2p-ca15-tc2.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/vexpress-v2p-ca15-tc2.dts
index 423629f..e19187f 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/vexpress-v2p-ca15-tc2.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/vexpress-v2p-ca15-tc2.dts
@@ -123,7 +123,7 @@
 
 	memory@80000000 {
 		device_type = "memory";
-		reg = <0x80000000 0x40000000>;
+		reg = <0x80000000 0x80000000>;
 	};
 
 	wdt@2a490000 {
